    "Samples were obtained using standard-of-care procedures.",
    "The samples were embedded fresh in Scigen Tissue-Plus O.C.T.",
    "Compound (Fisher Scientific) and stored at -80 °C before sectioning.",
    "Cryosections (10 μm) were mounted on Visium spatial gene expression slides (10x Genomics, 1000184).",
    "Two individual tumors were mounted in duplicate on the four 6.5-mm × 6.5-mm capture areas."
